# Design System

## ยง 3.1 Color Palette

**Applicable to all pages unless directed otherwise**

| Token | Color | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| Main Background | `#222831` | Page backgrounds |
| Section/Div | `#31363f` | Cards, modals, containers |
| Primary Text | `#76abae` | Main text, headings |
| Secondary Text | `#eeeeee` | Subheadings, labels |
| Button Background | `#31363f` | Button fills |
| Button Text | `#eeeeee` | Button labels |
| Button Hover | `#415780` | Hover states |

## ยง 3.2 Styling

- `border-radius: 0.35rem;` for all rounded elements
- Use Tailwind utilities when possible
- CSS variables for colors in global styles

## ยง 3.3 Buttons/Icons

- All buttons should be icons unless text is requested
- Use only icons from `$lib/icons/` folder
- All icon buttons must have `aria-label`
- Follow color rules based on placement (navbar, toolbar, modals)

## ยง 3.4 Accessibility

- Semantic HTML elements (`nav`, `main`, `section`, `article`)
- ARIA labels on interactive elements
- Keyboard navigation support (`tabindex`, `on:keydown`)
- Screen reader announcements via `aria-live="polite"`
- Focus states with visible outlines
